******************************
*      mc mod installer      *
******************************

Here's how to use it:
    [Arguments]
        (no arguments)              Runs the installer normally
        --addRepo [link to repo]    Adds a repository to the modpack menu
        --listRepos                 Lists your current repositories
        --removeRepo [repo number]  Remoes a repo from your menu
                                    (get repo number from --listRepos command)
